txt.en: Corrupted Gondorian Soliders can be found deep within Anglach: The Great Foundry.\n\nYou should put these poor souls to rest.
Gondorian soldiers have fallen to the corruption within Anglach. An adventurer is needed to brave the depths and put these poor souls to rest.

A notice hangs from the board, stamped with the royal seal of Gondor:

'It has been discovered that some of Captain Lachír's men remain in Anglach, corrupted beyond hope. It is with sadness we request an adventurer enter Anglach and put these poor souls to rest. Seek out Candúr at the Udûn Foothold for passage into Anglach.'

<rgb=#FF0000>Warning: This quest requires Anglach: The Great Foundry to be underway. If that quest has been completed or failed, you will be unable enter this instance in order to complete this quest.</rgb>
